comments: Langford (BOS) moves into Goodwin (ATL) and initiates contact that affects his driving shot attempt.
Smart (BOS) establishes his position in Goodwin's (ATL) path while setting the screen and absorbs the contact.
Tatum (BOS) briefly grasps and releases Hunter's (ATL) jersey off ball.
Collins (ATL) jumps from A to B into Tatum (BOS) and initiates contact that affects his shot attempt.
Collins (ATL) sets the screen on Tatum (BOS) and absorbs the contact.
Walker (BOS) moves laterally into Collins's (ATL) path and is not established in a legal guarding position when contact occurs.
Williams (BOS) makes marginal contact with Goodwin's (ATL) arm during his play at the basket.
Goodwin (ATL) makes contact with Walker's (BOS) arm and affects his SQBR.
Collins (ATL) sets the screen on Tatum (BOS) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Huerter (ATL) maintains a legal guarding position on Smart (BOS) during the drive.
Goodwin (ATL) makes marginal contact with Smart (BOS) during the loose ball.
Carter (ATL) sets the screen on Langford (BOS) and absorbs the contact.
Langford (BOS) maintains a legal guarding position during the jump shot attempt by Huerter (ATL).
Collins (ATL) and Smart (BOS) briefly engage and disengage during the rebound.
Huerter (ATL) commits a take foul on Langford (BOS).
